  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study to evaluate PF-04449913 (an inhibitor of the Hedgehog pathway) in Acute
      Myeloid Leukemia and high-risk Myelodysplastic Syndrome in combination with standard agents
      used to treat these diseases.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
